    <item>
      <title>美国警告中国将采取协调行动反对俄罗斯的战争支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/us-warns-china-of-coordinated-action-against-russian-war-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名美国高级官员周五表示，美国将与盟友协调，惩罚帮助俄罗斯加强军工基础的中国企业，包括可能对金融机构实施制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/us-warns-china-of-coordinated-action-against-russian-war-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 20:41:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登施压 以色列和哈马斯表示愿意停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-raises-pressure-on-israel-hamas-for-deal-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯对总统乔·拜登详细提出的以色列停火提议表示赞赏，这表明可能达成协议，结束该地区的血腥冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-raises-pressure-on-israel-hamas-for-deal-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 18:22:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登谴责特朗普在具有里程碑意义的判决后对法庭的攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-condemns-trump-attacks-on-court-after-landmark-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登严厉批评共和党对手唐纳德·特朗普对纽约一家法庭的攻击，该法庭在一场因支付封口费而判定他有罪的刑事审判中，拜登称这些攻击有可能破坏美国司法体系的稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/biden-condemns-trump-attacks-on-court-after-landmark-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 17:38:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普 2024 年竞选总统期间的法律案件时间表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普正在竞选重返白宫，同时面临多项迫在眉睫的刑事和民事审判——这是美国历史上其他候选人从未面临过的挑战。这些法律时间表有助于理解这一切]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/graphics/2024-trump-trials-court-dates-legal-timeline/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Mar 2024 10:00:29 GMT</pubDate>
